  -- ‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź Normal form types using our general DNF/CNF ‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź

  -- An "orthogonal normal form" is either:
  -- (a) A joinForm: g_n‚āĀ ‚ą® g_n‚āā ‚ą® ... ‚ą® g_n‚āĖ (DNF with single positive literal per clause)
  -- (b) A meetNegForm: ¬¨g_n‚āĀ ‚ąß ¬¨g_n‚āā ‚ąß ... ‚ąß ¬¨g_n‚āĖ (CNF with single negative literal per clause)
  data OrthoNF : Type‚āÄ where
    orthoJoin    : List ‚Ąē ‚Üí OrthoNF
    orthoMeetNeg : List ‚Ąē ‚Üí OrthoNF

  -- Join of generators: g_n‚āĀ ‚ą® g_n‚āā ‚ą® ...
  finJoin : List ‚Ąē ‚Üí ‚ü® B ‚ü©
  finJoin [] = ūĚüėB
  finJoin (n ‚ą∑ ns) = gen n ‚ą®B finJoin ns

  -- Meet of negated generators: ¬¨g_n‚āĀ ‚ąß ¬¨g_n‚āā ‚ąß ...
  finMeetNeg : List ‚Ąē ‚Üí ‚ü® B ‚ü©
  finMeetNeg [] = ūĚüôB
  finMeetNeg (n ‚ą∑ ns) = (¬¨B (gen n)) ‚ąßB finMeetNeg ns

  evalOrthoNF : OrthoNF ‚Üí ‚ü® B ‚ü©
  evalOrthoNF (orthoJoin ns) = finJoin ns
  evalOrthoNF (orthoMeetNeg ns) = finMeetNeg ns

  -- Bridge to general DNF/CNF evaluation
  finJoin‚Č°evalDNF : (ns : List ‚Ąē) ‚Üí finJoin ns ‚Č° evalDNF (joinFormDNF ns)
  finJoin‚Č°evalDNF [] = refl
  finJoin‚Č°evalDNF (n ‚ą∑ ns) =
    gen n ‚ą®B finJoin ns
      ‚Č°‚ü® cong (gen n ‚ą®B_) (finJoin‚Č°evalDNF ns) ‚ü©
    gen n ‚ą®B evalDNF (joinFormDNF ns)
      ‚Č°‚ü® cong (_‚ą®B evalDNF (joinFormDNF ns)) (sym (BR.¬∑IdR (gen n))) ‚ü©
    (gen n ‚ąßB ūĚüôB) ‚ą®B evalDNF (joinFormDNF ns) ‚ąé

  finMeetNeg‚Č°evalCNF : (ns : List ‚Ąē) ‚Üí finMeetNeg ns ‚Č° evalCNF (meetNegFormCNF ns)
  finMeetNeg‚Č°evalCNF [] = refl
  finMeetNeg‚Č°evalCNF (n ‚ą∑ ns) =
    (¬¨B (gen n)) ‚ąßB finMeetNeg ns
      ‚Č°‚ü® cong ((¬¨B (gen n)) ‚ąßB_) (finMeetNeg‚Č°evalCNF ns) ‚ü©
    (¬¨B (gen n)) ‚ąßB evalCNF (meetNegFormCNF ns)
      ‚Č°‚ü® cong (_‚ąßB evalCNF (meetNegFormCNF ns)) (sym BA.‚ą®IdR) ‚ü©
    ((¬¨B (gen n)) ‚ą®B ūĚüėB) ‚ąßB evalCNF (meetNegFormCNF ns) ‚ąé

  -- ‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź List operations for orthogonal normal forms ‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź

  _‚ąą?_ : ‚Ąē ‚Üí List ‚Ąē ‚Üí Bool
  n ‚ąą? [] = false
  n ‚ąą? (m ‚ą∑ ms) with discrete‚Ąē n m
