    finJoin ns
      ‚Č°‚ü® sym BA.¬¨Invol ‚ü©
    ¬¨B (¬¨B (finJoin ns))
      ‚Č°‚ü® cong ¬¨B_ (sym (deMorgan-finMeetNeg ns)) ‚ü©
    ¬¨B (finMeetNeg ns) ‚ąé

  -- Generator membership and absorption lemmas
  gen-in-finJoin : (n : ‚Ąē) (ms : List ‚Ąē) ‚Üí (n ‚ąą? ms) ‚Č° true ‚Üí
