  finMeetNeg-++ : (ns ms : List ‚Ąē) ‚Üí finMeetNeg (ns ++ ms) ‚Č° finMeetNeg ns ‚ąßB finMeetNeg ms
  finMeetNeg-++ [] ms = sym (BR.¬∑IdL (finMeetNeg ms))
