    (¬¨B (gen n)) ‚ąßB (finMeetNeg ns ‚ąßB finMeetNeg ms)
      ‚Č°‚ü® BR.¬∑Assoc (¬¨B (gen n)) (finMeetNeg ns) (finMeetNeg ms) ‚ü©
