  -- ‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź Ring identities for XOR with negation ‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź

  -- ¬¨a + b = a + ¬¨b  (negation can hop across XOR)
  ¬¨+b‚Č°a+¬¨ : (a b : ‚ü® B ‚ü©) ‚Üí BR._+_ (¬¨B a) b ‚Č° BR._+_ a (¬¨B b)
  ¬¨+b‚Č°a+¬¨ a b =
    BR._+_ (BR._+_ ūĚüôB a) b
      ‚Č°‚ü® cong (őĽ z ‚Üí BR._+_ z b) (BR.+Comm ūĚüôB a) ‚ü©
    BR._+_ (BR._+_ a ūĚüôB) b
      ‚Č°‚ü® sym (BR.+Assoc a ūĚüôB b) ‚ü©
